Resource.name: ReturnsService
Resource.Summary: This API enables you to invoke the interfaces defined on 'ReturnsService'.

Function.Description: Invoke the method 'GetApprovalTemplates' on this service by specifying the payload 'Document' in the JSON format.
Invoke the method 'HandleApprovalRequest' on this service.

DataTypes.Description: The 'DataTypes' defines the types referenced by the 'Functions'. It is only for QA, not for info dev.
